#: Templates/identify/register.html:104
msgid "Acceptance of Terms"
msgstr "Acceptació dels Termes"

#: Templates/identify/register.html:105
msgid ""
"By creating an account on StreamSync, you agree to comply with and be bound "
"by these Terms and Conditions."
msgstr "En crear un compte a StreamSync, accepteu complir i estar vinculat per aquests Termes i Condicions."

#: Templates/identify/register.html:107
msgid "Use of the Service"
msgstr "Ús del Servei"

#: Templates/identify/register.html:108
msgid ""
"You agree to use the service only for lawful purposes. You are responsible "
"for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials."
msgstr "Accepteu utilitzar el servei només amb finalitats lícites. Sou responsable de mantenir la confidencialitat de les vostres credencials del compte."

#: Templates/identify/register.html:111
msgid ""
"Your privacy is important to us. Please review our Privacy Policy to "
"understand how we collect and use your data."
msgstr "La vostra privadesa és important per a nosaltres. Reviseu la nostra Política de Privadesa per entendre com recollim i utilitzem les vostres dades."

#: Templates/identify/register.html:113
msgid "Limitation of Liability"
msgstr "Limitació de Responsabilitat"

#: Templates/identify/register.html:114
msgid ""
"StreamSync is provided 'as is' without warranties of any kind. We are not "
"liable for any damages arising from the use of our service."
msgstr "StreamSync es proporciona 'tal qual' sense garanties de cap tipus. No ens fem responsables dels danys derivats de l'ús del nostre servei."

#: Templates/identify/register.html:116
msgid "Changes to Terms"
msgstr "Canvis als Termes"

#: Templates/identify/register.html:117
msgid ""
"We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Your continued use "
"of the service constitutes acceptance of the new terms."
msgstr "Ens reservem el dret de modificar aquests termes en qualsevol moment. El vostre ús continuat del servei constitueix l'acceptació dels nous termes."

